{"tid":2442361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【10.13 牛頭角】地政丈量員被控藏鐳射筆　判囚3個月　准保釋上訴","createTime":"2021-03-11T10:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:17:05.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7beaa93eb5912f7d801fdbb380d786a9afe5647e","tid":2442361,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"網民於 2019 年 10 月 13 日發起「 18 區開花」，多區爆發警民衝突。33 歲地政總署丈量員被控在牛頭角管有鐳射筆，經審訊後被定罪，今（8 日）在觀塘裁判法院判監3個月；辯方申請保釋以待就定罪上訴獲批。裁判官屈麗雯指出，雖然事件中無人因為鐳射筆而受傷，但它可以傷害他人眼睛，現場亦出現堵路，法庭不能忽視鐳射筆的危險性。<br />\n<br />\n被告未有在現場拿出鐳射筆，<span class=\"red\">警方亦指出鐳射筆是未經使用</span>，案發現場附近亦只有路障，沒有暴力或損害財物的情況。<br />\n<br />\n辯方隨即表示將就定罪提出上訴，並申請保釋候訊；最終被告獲准以現金 2 萬元保釋、候訊期間不得離港、交出所有旅遊證件、每天到警署報到一次以及居於報稱地址。"},{"pid":"eecd37bfb538fc21d476950ee2575ebc5b0e45bd","tid":2442361,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-13-%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92-%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%88%E9%87%8F%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-13-%25E7%2589%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E4%25B8%2588%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A3%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=e1b08fb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-13-%25E7%2589%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E4%25B8%2588%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A3%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&h=0c6182cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-13-%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92-%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%88%E9%87%8F%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4/</a>"},{"pid":"e1699ffb71b4aabd9341bc763a4dc8bb330c29d1","tid":2442361,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"丈量員有鐳射筆幾咁出奇啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74c34a68ebd5331f3476305ea9e8f0f006a67c2","tid":2442361,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"之前報導<br />\n<br />\n辯方指出，陳在案發當日撰寫的口供稱「該男子行入遊樂場的一條支路，本人上前拘捕」，辯方質疑當時陳形容被告是「行」，而非庭上的「跑」，又指陳在該口供沒有提及被告氣喘，以及在被告銀包搜出一張測量員員工證；陳均同意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-13-%E7%89%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%A7%92-%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%88%E9%87%8F%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86-%E8%AD%A6-%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E5%A4%AA%E4%B9%85%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A-%E5%83%85%E8%A8%98%E5%BE%97%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-13-%25E7%2589%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E4%25B8%2588%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E4%25B9%2585%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A-%25E5%2583%2585%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25AD%2597%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=dc02a451\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-13-%25E7%25